tasks.description: React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'dispatch' and 'grouppedTasks'. Either include them or remove the dependency array
Исправить названия колонок и столбцов в хаотичном порядке

ASssignments to the 'grouppedTasks' variable from inside React Hook useEffect will be lost after each render. To preserve the value over time, store it in a useRef Hook and keep the mutable value in the '.current' property.
